Installation instructions

    git clone git://github.com/bbarcesaj125/vim-dot.git ~/.vim

Creating Symbolic links

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Installing plugins as submodules

	cd ~/.vim
	git submodule add http://github.com/someuser/someplugin.git bundle/someplugin
	git add .
	git commit -m "Install someplugin.vim bundle as a submodule."
